            <thetext>fixed on trunk with rev. 23919

the problem was that, when dragging portlet from left to right, the checking was done on the left property of the dragged box against the left property of the groupbox. instead it should be done on left+width.

on the other browsers it worked because dragging also scrolled the viewport horizontally and the user could get the chance to position it better over the new groupbox.</thetext>
